all:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-1 fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-one\" style=\"--awb-text-color:#000f98;--awb-sep-color:#000f98;--awb-font-size:30px;\"><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-left\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000f98;\"><\/div><\/div><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><h1 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-center\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Be Vietnam Pro&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;margin:0;font-size:1em;\">VINHOMES H\u1ea2I V\u00c2N BAY<\/h1><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-right\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000f98;\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-1\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p><strong>Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong> l\u00e0 si\u00eau d\u1ef1 \u00e1n <strong>&#8220;th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng&#8221;<\/strong> quy m\u00f4 512 hecta v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 44.000 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00e8o H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n &#8211; \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, do T\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Vingroup ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng &#8211; \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb cao c\u1ea5p s\u1edf h\u1eefu 5.928 c\u0103n bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 th\u1ea5p t\u1ea7ng \u0111a phong c\u00e1ch, v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 90% s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ph\u00e1p l\u00fd s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng mi\u1ec1n Trung. <strong>Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong> mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 sinh l\u1eddi b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian an c\u01b0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho nh\u1eefng gia \u0111\u00ecnh tinh hoa khao kh\u00e1t phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nguy\u00ean b\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-2 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" alt=\"Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay - n\u01a1i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 tinh hoa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 an c\u01b0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh tinh hoa v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c\" title=\"Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay &#8211; n\u01a1i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 tinh hoa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 an c\u01b0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh tinh hoa v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Vinhomes-Hai-Van-Bay-noi-hoi-tu-tinh-hoa-thien-nhien-va-dang-cap-song-hien-dai-mo-ra-co-hoi-dau-tu-va-an-cu-ly-tuong-cho-cac