 Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb phong th\u1ee7y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. <strong data-start=\"1738\" data-end=\"1750\">Ph\u00eda B\u1eafc<\/strong> d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u00e0 d\u00e3y n\u00fai H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n h\u00f9ng v\u0129, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201ct\u1ea5m b\u00ecnh phong t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean\u201d b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. <strong data-start=\"1831\" data-end=\"1851\">Ph\u00eda Nam v\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng<\/strong> m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng ra v\u1ecbnh Nam Ch\u01a1n, \u0111\u00f3n tr\u1ecdn sinh kh\u00ed t\u1eeb bi\u1ec3n c\u1ea3. <strong data-start=\"1908\" data-end=\"1920\">Ph\u00eda T\u00e2y<\/strong> k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c khu d\u00e2n c\u01b0, h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a qu\u1eadn Li\u00ean Chi\u1ec3u, t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nguy\u00ean s\u01a1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2072\" data-end=\"2453\">\u0110\u1ecba h\u00ecnh b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1edbi ba m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n gi\u00fap d\u1ef1 \u00e1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edd bi\u1ec3n d\u00e0i c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3nh quan \u0111a d\u1ea1ng: b\u00e3i c\u00e1t tr\u1eafng m\u1ecbn, c\u00e1c m\u0169i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, r\u1eebng c\u00e2y nguy\u00ean sinh v\u00e0 h\u1ed3 c\u1ea3nh quan. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n mang l\u1ea1i ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng phong th\u1ee7y d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o \u2013 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t coi tr\u1ecdng khi ch\u1ecdn n\u01a1i an c\u01b0, ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-4 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1280\" height=\"806\" alt=\"Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ba m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n, bao quanh b\u1edfi n\u00fai H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n h\u00f9ng v\u0129, m\u1edf ra kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng chu\u1ea9n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nguy\u00ean s\u01a1.\" title=\"vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5446\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271280%27%20height%3D%27806%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201280%20806%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271280%27%20height%3D%27806%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg-200x126.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg-400x252.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg-600x378.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg-800x504.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg-1200x756.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg.jpg 1280w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-9\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ba m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n, bao quanh b\u1edfi n\u00fai H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n h\u00f9ng v\u0129, m\u1edf ra kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng chu\u1ea9n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nguy\u00ean s\u01a1.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-10\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><h3 data-start=\"2455\" data-end=\"2489\">K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng \u2013 giao th\u00f4ng<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2490\" data-end=\"2741\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i giao th\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. D\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u1eb1m ngay c\u1eeda ng\u00f5 T\u00e2y B\u1eafc \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, tr\u00ean tr\u1ee5c giao th\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean k\u1ebft B\u1eafc \u2013 Nam, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u1ec3n \u2013 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ed9 \u2013 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eaft \u2013 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2743\" data-end=\"3369\">\n<li data-start=\"2743\" data-end=\"2915\">\n<p data-start=\"2745\" data-end=\"2915\"><strong data-start=\"2745\" data-end=\"2768\">Trong v\u00f2ng 10 ph\u00fat:<\/strong> c\u01b0 d\u00e2n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn C\u1ea3ng Li\u00ean Chi\u1ec3u \u2013 trung t\u00e2m logistics qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, v\u00e0 ga Kim Li\u00ean \u2013 ga h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eaft B\u1eafc \u2013 Nam.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2916\" data-end=\"3082\">\n<p data-start=\"2918\" data-end=\"3082\"><strong data-start=\"2918\" data-end=\"2941\">Trong v\u00f2ng 15 ph\u00fat:<\/strong> ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn h\u1ea7m H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n 1 &amp; 2 \u2013 c\u1eeda ng\u00f5 giao th\u01b0\u01a1ng huy\u1ebft m\u1ea1ch k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u1edbi Th\u1eeba Thi\u00ean Hu\u1ebf; c\u00f9ng trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh qu\u1eadn Li\u00ean Chi\u1ec3u.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3083\" data-end=\"3227\">\n<p data-start=\"3085\" data-end=\"3227\"><strong data-start=\"3085\" data-end=\"3108\">Trong v\u00f2ng 20 ph\u00fat:<\/strong> \u0111\u1ebfn trung t\u00e2m th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u2013 n\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung kinh t\u1ebf, v\u0103n h\u00f3a, ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb; s\u00e2n bay qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng; v\u00e0 ga \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3228\" data-end=\"3369\">\n<p data-start=\"3230\" data-end=\"3369\"><strong data-start=\"3230\" data-end=\"3253\">Trong v\u00f2ng 35 ph\u00fat:<\/strong> kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u1ed9i An, c\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4 Hu\u1ebf, c\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn sinh th\u00e1i nh\u01b0 su\u1ed1i L\u01b0\u01a1ng, R\u1ea1n Nam \u00d4, b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n L\u0103ng C\u00f4.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3371\" data-end=\"3666\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n g\u1ed3m cao t\u1ed1c La S\u01a1n \u2013 T\u00fay Loan, h\u1ea7m H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n 2, tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ven bi\u1ec3n Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5t Th\u00e0nh n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i c\u00e0ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c cho d\u1ef1 \u00e1n. Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho an c\u01b0, ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec3m trung chuy\u1ec3n k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i du l\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-11\"><p data-start=\"3689\" data-end=\"3949\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea5t ven bi\u1ec3n ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khan hi\u1ebfm, Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3. Ba m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n, l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao b\u1ecdc b\u1edfi d\u00e3y n\u00fai H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n, d\u1ef1 \u00e1n mang gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9c b\u1ea3n \u2013 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng theo th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3951\" data-end=\"4406\">\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh <strong data-start=\"4018\" data-end=\"4078\">trung t\u00e2m t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 du l\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf<\/strong>. C\u1ea3ng Li\u00ean Chi\u1ec3u, s\u00e2n bay qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 \u00e1n h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng quy m\u00f4 l\u1edbn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t tri\u1ec3n khai s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn khu v\u1ef1c T\u00e2y B\u1eafc, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ecbnh L\u00e0ng V\u00e2n, th\u00e0nh \u201ct\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0ng\u201d thu h\u00fat d\u00f2ng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00e0 c\u00f2n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n cho gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-5 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1280\" height=\"804\" alt=\"V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecba th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c b\u1ea3n hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3, Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean ng\u1ecdc qu\u00fd gi\u1eefa l\u00f2ng \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb phong th\u1ee7y, v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c h\u00fat m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd cho nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0.\" title=\"vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5445\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271280%27%20height%3D%27804%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201280%20804%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271280%27%20height%3D%27804%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg-200x126.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg-400x251.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg-600x377.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg-800x503.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg-1200x754.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg.jpg 1280w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-12\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecba th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c b\u1ea3n hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3, Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean ng\u1ecdc qu\u00fd gi\u1eefa l\u00f2ng \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb phong th\u1ee7y, v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c h\u00fat m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd cho nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-13\"><p data-start=\"4436\" data-end=\"4900\">V\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ecba l\u00fd hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3, c\u1ea3nh quan thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o, Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 hai gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb: cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i sinh l\u1eddi b\u1ec1n v\u1eefn<strong data-start=\"4579\" data-end=\"4631\">g<\/strong>. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u01b0 d\u00e2n, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng trong l\u00e0nh, h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, n\u01a1i m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0, d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1edf ra ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng gia t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1edd v\u1ecb tr\u00ed chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u uy t\u00edn Vingroup.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"4902\" data-end=\"5248\">Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1eddi khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed <strong>Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong> ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u201cc\u1eeda ng\u00f5 thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng, phong th\u1ee7y v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng kinh t\u1ebf. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 an c\u01b0 \u2013 ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a mi\u1ec1n Trung, n\u01a1i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-5 fusion-flex-container hundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-padding-right:0px;--awb-padding-left:0px;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"width:104% !important;max-width:104% !important;margin-left: calc(-4% \/ 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% \/ 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-9 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-6 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background hundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"width:104% !important;max-width:104% !important;margin-left: calc(-4% \/ 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% \/ 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-10 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:20px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-5 fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:20px;--awb-font-size:22px;\"><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-left\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-center\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Be Vietnam Pro&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;margin:0;font-size:1em;\">TI\u1ec6N \u00cdCH VINHOMES H\u1ea2I V\u00c2N BAY \u0110\u00c0 N\u1eb4NG<\/h2><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-right\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-14\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>Trong quy ho\u1ea1ch 512ha b\u00ean v\u1ecbnh L\u00e0ng V\u00e2n, <strong data-start=\"331\" data-end=\"355\">Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong> kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p k\u00edn v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i ti\u1ec7n \u00edch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o theo m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u201call-in-one\u201d \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Vinhomes, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n, n\u01a1i m\u1ed7i b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m 5 sao.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-15\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>Ti\u1ec7n \u00edch t\u1ea1i Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean n\u00fai \u2013 bi\u1ec3n h\u00f9ng v\u0129 v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n kh\u00f4ng khai th\u00e1c \u1ed3 \u1ea1t, m\u00e0 d\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn di\u1ec7n t\u00edch cho kh\u00f4ng gian xanh, c\u1ea3nh quan m\u1eb7t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh c\u00f4ng c\u1ed9ng. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n v\u1eeba t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n s\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n nghi, v\u1eeba c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng sinh th\u00e1i b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u201cchu\u1ea9n s\u1ed1ng Vinhomes\u201d m\u00e0 kh\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e0o s\u00e1nh k\u1ecbp.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-7 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" alt=\"Vincom Center Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u2013 trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng, h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 mua s\u1eafm, \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed cao c\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng tinh hoa.\" title=\"vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5444\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201920%201080%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-16\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Vincom Center Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u2013 trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng, h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 mua s\u1eafm, \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed cao c\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng tinh hoa.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-17\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p data-start=\"1208\" data-end=\"1611\">N\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t trong h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i ti\u1ec7n \u00edch l\u00e0 <strong data-start=\"1252\" data-end=\"1277\">b\u1ebfn du thuy\u1ec1n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf<\/strong> quy m\u00f4 l\u1edbn, n\u01a1i c\u01b0 d\u00e2n v\u00e0 du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn h\u1ea3i tr\u00ecnh xa hoa ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u gi\u1eefa l\u00e0n n\u01b0\u1edbc xanh bi\u1ebfc. K\u1ec1 b\u00ean l\u00e0 <strong data-start=\"1451\" data-end=\"1472\">s\u00e2n golf ven bi\u1ec3n<\/strong> chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, v\u1eeba mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn h\u01b0\u1edbng bi\u1ec3n ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-8 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" alt=\"B\u1ebfn du thuy\u1ec1n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u2013 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1eb9n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u, n\u01a1i c\u01b0 d\u00e2n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m du l\u1ecbch bi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ngay t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.\" title=\"ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5443\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201920%201080%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-18\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">B\u1ebfn du thuy\u1ec1n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u2013 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1eb9n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u, n\u01a1i c\u01b0 d\u00e2n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m du l\u1ecbch bi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ngay t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-19\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng <strong data-start=\"1660\" data-end=\"1698\">kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao, resort ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng<\/strong>, trung t\u00e2m <strong data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1728\">spa &amp; wellness<\/strong> ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, khu <strong data-start=\"1784\" data-end=\"1801\">gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed bi\u1ec3n<\/strong> v\u1edbi \u0111a d\u1ea1ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 l\u01b0\u1edbt s\u00f3ng, ch\u00e8o sup, l\u1eb7n ng\u1eafm san h\u00f4, kayak\u2026 s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t khu v\u1ef1c.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-9 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" alt=\"S\u00e2n golf ven bi\u1ec3n mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ec3 thao sang tr\u1ecdng, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3nh quan n\u00fai \u2013 bi\u1ec3n h\u00f9ng v\u0129 hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 t\u1ea1i mi\u1ec1n Trung.\" title=\"san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5442\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201920%201080%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-20\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">S\u00e2n golf ven bi\u1ec3n mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ec3 thao sang tr\u1ecdng, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3nh quan n\u00fai \u2013 bi\u1ec3n h\u00f9ng v\u0129 hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 t\u1ea1i mi\u1ec1n Trung.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-21\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nhu c\u1ea7u mua s\u1eafm \u2013 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi <strong data-start=\"2047\" data-end=\"2064\">Vincom Center<\/strong>, <strong data-start=\"2066\" data-end=\"2096\">ph\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u2013 shophouse<\/strong> ven bi\u1ec3n, c\u00f9ng khu <strong data-start=\"2116\" data-end=\"2146\">\u1ea9m th\u1ef1c qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecba<\/strong>. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i mua s\u1eafm, th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m v\u0103n h\u00f3a \u2013 gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, thu h\u00fat du kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i cho d\u1ef1 \u00e1n.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-10 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1081\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean ven bi\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n xanh m\u00e1t, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.\" title=\"cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5441\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271081%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201920%201081%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271081%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg-1200x676.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg.jpg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-22\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean ven bi\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n xanh m\u00e1t, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-23\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>V\u1ec1 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c \u2013 y t\u1ebf, Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay t\u00edch h\u1ee3p <strong data-start=\"2351\" data-end=\"2379\">tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Vinschool<\/strong> v\u00e0 <strong data-start=\"2383\" data-end=\"2403\">b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n Vinmec<\/strong>, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 an t\u00e2m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i cho c\u01b0 d\u00e2n. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3, d\u1ef1 \u00e1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ed1ng d\u00e0i l\u00e2u cho c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-24\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p data-start=\"2589\" data-end=\"2980\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u2013 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. M\u00f4 h\u00ecnh qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chu\u1ea9n Vinhomes k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 AI, IoT trong gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh, gi\u00fap c\u01b0 d\u00e2n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng an to\u00e0n, th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n. An ninh \u0111a l\u1edbp 24\/7 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 ri\u00eang t\u01b0 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i cho m\u1ed7i gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2982\" data-end=\"3231\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch t\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh theo chu\u1ea9n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao. T\u1eeb l\u1ec5 t\u00e2n, d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ea3nh quan \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eb7t tour, \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e9, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ea9n h\u00f3a, mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho c\u01b0 d\u00e2n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ed1ng ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-11 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2200\" height=\"1238\" alt=\"H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t an ninh, an to\u00e0n 24\/7.\" title=\"H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t an ninh, an to\u00e0n 24\/7.\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5048\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%272200%27%20height%3D%271238%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%202200%201238%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%272200%27%20height%3D%271238%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247.jpg 2200w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-25\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t an ninh, an to\u00e0n 24\/7.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-26\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p data-start=\"3257\" data-end=\"3557\">H\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i ti\u1ec7n \u00edch 5 sao t\u1ea1i Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u sinh ho\u1ea1t, ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1ee7a c\u01b0 d\u00e2n, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gia t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0. M\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh thanh kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng sinh l\u1eddi d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3559\" data-end=\"3990\">Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, s\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa ti\u1ec7n \u00edch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh quan sinh th\u00e1i n\u00fai \u2013 bi\u1ec3n bi\u1ebfn n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y th\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3. C\u01b0 d\u00e2n v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n b\u00ecnh minh tr\u00ean b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n ri\u00eang, v\u1eeba th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n trong c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean xanh, ch\u01a1i golf bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u hay mua s\u1eafm t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i s\u1ea7m u\u1ea5t. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i mi\u1ec1n Trung.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3992\" data-end=\"4251\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, <strong data-start=\"4004\" data-end=\"4028\">Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong> kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201cthi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch\u201d kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p s\u1ed1ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn d\u1ef1 \u00e1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng tinh hoa trong n\u0103m 2025.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-7 fusion-flex-container hundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-