13 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:20px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-7 fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-font-size:18px;\"><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-left\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-center\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Be Vietnam Pro&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;margin:0;font-size:1em;\">PH\u00c2N KHU CH\u00c2U \u00c2U<\/h3><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-right\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-31\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>Khu Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb l\u00e0 \u201cc\u1eeda ng\u00f5\u201d c\u1ee7a <strong data-start=\"240\" data-end=\"264\">Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong>, n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i ph\u00eda T\u00e2y Nam d\u1ef1 \u00e1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ph\u00e2n khu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u01b0 d\u00e2n v\u00e0 du kh\u00e1ch, mang trong m\u00ecnh vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-15 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1563\" height=\"879\" alt=\"D\u1ef1 \u00e1n Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng n\u01a1i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 tinh hoa ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac, thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o chu\u1ea9n s\u1ed1ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ngay t\u1ea1i v\u1ecbnh Nam Ch\u01a1n.\" title=\"Du-an-vinhomes-hai-van-da-nang-kien-truc-thien-nhien-quan-ly-van-hanh-hien-dai-chuan-song-quoc-te-vinh-nam-chon\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Du-an-vinhomes-hai-van-da-nang-kien-truc-thien-nhien-quan-ly-van-hanh-hien-dai-chuan-song-quoc-te-vinh-nam-chon.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Du-an-vinhomes-hai-van-da-nang-kien-truc-thien-nhien-quan-ly-van-hanh-hien-dai-chuan-song-quoc-te-vinh-nam-chon.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5435\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271563%27%20height%3D%27879%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201563%20879%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271563%27%20height%3D%27879%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Du-an-vinhomes-hai-van-da-nang-kien-truc-thien-nhien-quan-ly-van-hanh-hien-dai-chuan-song-quoc-te-vinh-nam-chon-200x112.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Du-an-vinhomes-hai-van-da-nang-kien-truc-thien-nhien-quan-ly-van-hanh-hien-dai-chuan-song-quoc-te-vinh-nam-chon-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Du-an-vinhomes-hai-van-da-nang-kien-truc-thien-nhien-quan-ly-van-hanh-hien-dai-chuan-song-quoc-te-vinh-nam-chon-600x337.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Du-an-vinhomes-hai-van-da-nang-kien-truc-thien-nhien-quan-ly-van-hanh-hien-dai-chuan-song-quoc-te-vinh-nam-chon-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Du-an-vinhomes-hai-van-da-nang-kien-truc-thien-nhien-quan-ly-van-hanh-hien-dai-chuan-song-quoc-te-vinh-nam-chon-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Du-an-vinhomes-hai-van-da-nang-kien-truc-thien-nhien-quan-ly-van-hanh-hien-dai-chuan-song-quoc-te-vinh-nam-chon.jpg 1563w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-32\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">D\u1ef1 \u00e1n Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng n\u01a1i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 tinh hoa ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac, thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o chu\u1ea9n s\u1ed1ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ngay t\u1ea1i v\u1ecbnh Nam Ch\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-33\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a khu Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 2.668 c\u0103n h\u1ed9 li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1 (62\u201365m\u00b2), tr\u00ean 400 c\u0103n shophouse (90m\u00b2) c\u00f9ng 850 c\u0103n song l\u1eadp. Ngo\u00e0i ra, ph\u00e2n khu c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c t\u00f2a cao t\u1ea7ng d\u00e0nh cho nh\u00e0 \u1edf x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng nhu c\u1ea7u sinh s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 kinh doanh. V\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn phong c\u00e1ch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn ph\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cph\u1ed1 \u0111i b\u1ed9\u201d s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng, h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 chu\u1ed7i c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng mua s\u1eafm, \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, mang l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ed1ng chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ngay gi\u1eefa l\u00f2ng mi\u1ec1n Trung.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-34\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 kinh doanh, khu Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn trung t\u00e2m th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3ng Li\u00ean Chi\u1ec3u \u2013 trung t\u00e2m logistics qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, m\u1edf ra ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd cho c\u1ea3 c\u01b0 d\u00e2n v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-35\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>Nh\u1edd h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, ti\u1ec7n \u00edch v\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i, Khu 1 \u2013 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 <strong data-start=\"1451\" data-end=\"1473\">\u201ctr\u00e1i tim kinh t\u1ebf\u201d<\/strong> c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n d\u1ef1 \u00e1n. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung d\u00f2ng ch\u1ea3y th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u2013 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi mang l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i sinh l\u1eddi v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 shophouse v\u00e0 c\u0103n h\u1ed9 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 trong d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-10 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background hundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-background-color:#fba5b6;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"width:104% !important;max-width:104% !important;margin-left: calc(-4% \/ 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% \/ 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-14 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:20px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-8 fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-font-size:18px;\"><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-left\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-center\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Be Vietnam Pro&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;margin:0;font-size:1em;\">PH\u00c2N KHU CH\u00c2U \u00c1<\/h3><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-right\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-36\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>N\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m d\u1ef1 \u00e1n, <strong data-start=\"211\" data-end=\"225\">Khu Ch\u00e2u \u00c1<\/strong> s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ecba th\u1ebf \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba khi v\u1eeba ti\u1ebfp gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n, v\u1eeba t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c tr\u00ean cao, m\u1edf ra t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kho\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea1t v\u1ec1 v\u1ecbnh Nam Ch\u01a1n th\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 d\u00e3y n\u00fai H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n h\u00f9ng v\u0129. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ph\u00e2n khu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u201ctr\u00e1i tim ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng\u201d c\u1ee7a Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay, n\u01a1i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 tinh hoa ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-16 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" alt=\"Bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 bi\u1ec3n Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang phong c\u00e1ch ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, h\u1ed3 b\u01a1i ri\u00eang, s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn xanh m\u00e1t, mang l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ed1ng ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n.\" title=\"biet-thu-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-kien-truc-dang-cap-quoc-te-ho-boi-rieng-san-vuon-xanh-song-nghi-duong-tron-ven.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/biet-thu-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-kien-truc-dang-cap-quoc-te-ho-boi-rieng-san-vuon-xanh-song-nghi-duong-tron-ven.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/biet-thu-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-kien-truc-dang-cap-quoc-te-ho-boi-rieng-san-vuon-xanh-song-nghi-duong-tron-ven.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5438\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201920%201080%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/biet-thu-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-kien-truc-dang-cap-quoc-te-ho-boi-rieng-san-vuon-xanh-song-nghi-duong-tron-ven.jpg-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/biet-thu-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-kien-truc-dang-cap-quoc-te-ho-boi-rieng-san-vuon-xanh-song-nghi-duong-tron-ven.jpg-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/biet-thu-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-kien-truc-dang-cap-quoc-te-ho-boi-rieng-san-vuon-xanh-song-nghi-duong-tron-ven.jpg-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/biet-thu-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-kien-truc-dang-cap-quoc-te-ho-boi-rieng-san-vuon-xanh-song-nghi-duong-tron-ven.jpg-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/biet-thu-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-kien-truc-dang-cap-quoc-te-ho-boi-rieng-san-vuon-xanh-song-nghi-duong-tron-ven.jpg-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/biet-thu-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-kien-truc-dang-cap-quoc-te-ho-boi-rieng-san-vuon-xanh-song-nghi-duong-tron-ven.jpg.jpg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-37\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 bi\u1ec3n Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang phong c\u00e1ch ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, h\u1ed3 b\u01a1i ri\u00eang, s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn xanh m\u00e1t, mang l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ed1ng ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-38\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u1ea5p, <strong>ph\u00e2n khu Th\u1ecbnh V\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/strong> mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho c\u01b0 d\u00e2n m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng, ri\u00eang t\u01b0 v\u00e0 y\u00ean t\u0129nh gi\u1eefa nh\u1ecbp s\u1ed1ng s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean xanh m\u00e1t v\u00e0 k\u00eanh \u0111\u00e0o n\u1ed9i khu r\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0i h\u00f2a v\u1edbi thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-39\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>Khu Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng 750 c\u0103n bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 cao c\u1ea5p, mang thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng Panorama view bi\u1ec3n \u2013 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1eb9n \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o d\u00e0nh cho gi\u1edbi tinh hoa. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ga t\u00e0u Railway v\u00e0 v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, c\u00f9ng chu\u1ed7i ti\u1ec7n \u00edch ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng chu\u1ea9n 5 sao, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1ed1ng ri\u00eang t\u01b0, t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-40\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 kh\u00e9p k\u00edn trong s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng, <strong data-start=\"1002\" data-end=\"1016\">Khu Ch\u00e2u \u00c1<\/strong> c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00e2n khu kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn b\u1ebfn du thuy\u1ec1n, trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i hay c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean ven bi\u1ec3n \u2013 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch cao c\u1ea5p m\u00e0 Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang \u0111\u1ebfn.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-41\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong quy ho\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m, Khu Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb l\u00e0<strong data-start=\"1309\" data-end=\"1367\"> \u201cthi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 bi\u1ec3n\u201d<\/strong> c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i an c\u01b0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u v\u00e0 bi\u1ec7t l\u1eadp, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ven bi\u1ec3n \u2013 ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khan hi\u1ebfm v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb gia t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd theo th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-11 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background hundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-background-color:#fba5b6;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"width:104% !important;max-width:104% !important;margin-left: calc(-4% \/ 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% \/ 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-15 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:20px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-9 fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-font-size:18px;\"><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-left\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-center\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Be Vietnam Pro&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;margin:0;font-size:1em;\">PH\u00c2N KHU NH\u1eacT B\u1ea2N<\/h3><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-right\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-42\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>T\u1ecda l\u1ea1c t\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay, <strong data-start=\"228\" data-end=\"244\">Khu Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<\/strong> s\u1edf h\u1eefu v\u1ecb tr\u00ed chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c khi k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa ph\u00e2n khu Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ea7m u\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n khu Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 sang tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb tinh th\u1ea7n ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y mang \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, g\u1eafn k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa con ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u1ec7n \u00edch c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n d\u1ef1 \u00e1n.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-17 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1563\" height=\"879\" alt=\"Shophouse t\u1ea1i Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9, li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 \u0111i b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 khu gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m mua s\u1eafm v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cao c\u1ea5p ven bi\u1ec3n.\" title=\"shophouse-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-quy-hoach-dong-bo-lien-ke-pho-di-bo-khu-giai-tri-tam-diem-mua-sam-dich-vu-cao-cap-ven-bien.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/shophouse-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-quy-hoach-dong-bo-lien-ke-pho-di-bo-khu-giai-tri-tam-diem-mua-sam-dich-vu-cao-cap-ven-bien.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/shophouse-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-quy-hoach-dong-bo-lien-ke-pho-di-bo-khu-giai-tri-tam-diem-mua-sam-dich-vu-cao-cap-ven-bien.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5437\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271563%27%20height%3D%27879%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201563%20879%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271563%27%20height%3D%27879%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/shophouse-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-quy-hoach-dong-bo-lien-ke-pho-di-bo-khu-giai-tri-tam-diem-mua-sam-dich-vu-cao-cap-ven-bien.jpg-200x112.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/shophouse-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-quy-hoach-dong-bo-lien-ke-pho-di-bo-khu-giai-tri-tam-diem-mua-sam-dich-vu-cao-cap-ven-bien.jpg-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/shophouse-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-quy-hoach-dong-bo-lien-ke-pho-di-bo-khu-giai-tri-tam-diem-mua-sam-dich-vu-cao-cap-ven-bien.jpg-600x337.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/shophouse-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-quy-hoach-dong-bo-lien-ke-pho-di-bo-khu-giai-tri-tam-diem-mua-sam-dich-vu-cao-cap-ven-bien.jpg-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/shophouse-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-quy-hoach-dong-bo-lien-ke-pho-di-bo-khu-giai-tri-tam-diem-mua-sam-dich-vu-cao-cap-ven-bien.jpg-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/shophouse-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-quy-hoach-dong-bo-lien-ke-pho-di-bo-khu-giai-tri-tam-diem-mua-sam-dich-vu-cao-cap-ven-bien.jpg.jpg 1563w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-43\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Shophouse t\u1ea1i Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9, li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 \u0111i b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 khu gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m mua s\u1eafm v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cao c\u1ea5p ven bi\u1ec3n.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-44\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khu Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi <strong data-start=\"581\" data-end=\"616\">1.400 c\u0103n h\u1ed9 li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1 (60\u2013100m\u00b2)<\/strong>, h\u01a1n <strong data-start=\"622\" data-end=\"655\">600 c\u0103n shophouse (150\u2013200m\u00b2)<\/strong> c\u00f9ng <strong data-start=\"661\" data-end=\"701\">850 c\u0103n bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 \u0111\u01a1n l\u1eadp (200\u2013400m\u00b2)<\/strong>. \u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 <strong data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"763\">trung t\u00e2m ti\u1ec7n \u00edch quy m\u00f4 l\u1edbn<\/strong>, n\u01a1i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i, mua s\u1eafm, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cao c\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 c\u01b0 d\u00e2n l\u1eabn du kh\u00e1ch. C\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn ph\u1ed1 t\u1ea1i ph\u00e2n khu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo phong c\u00e1ch Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, v\u1eeba tinh gi\u1ea3n v\u1eeba tinh t\u1ebf, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng gi\u00e0u tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-45\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>T\u1eeb v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n <strong data-start=\"1072\" data-end=\"1088\">Khu Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<\/strong> d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ph\u00e2n khu kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec7n \u00edch tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean ven bi\u1ec3n, b\u1ebfn du thuy\u1ec1n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i Vincom hay s\u00e2n golf ven bi\u1ec3n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m giao thoa gi\u1eefa nh\u1ecbp s\u1ed1ng s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u01b0 th\u00e1i ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, mang l\u1ea1i gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-46\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tinh t\u1ebf, ti\u1ec7n \u00edch \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m, Khu Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201ctr\u00e1i tim ti\u1ec7n \u00edch\u201d c\u1ee7a <strong>Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong>. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ed1ng chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, ph\u00e2n khu n\u00e0y c\u00f2n m\u1edf ra ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng kinh doanh \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb gia t\u0103ng theo th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-12 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background hundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-background-color:#fba5b6;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"width:104% !important;max-width:104% !important;margin-left: calc(-4% \/ 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% \/ 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-16 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:20px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-10 fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-font-size:18px;\"><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-left\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-center\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Be Vietnam Pro&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;margin:0;font-size:1em;\">PH\u00c2N KHU MONACO<\/h3><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-right\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-47\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>N\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed bi\u1ec7t l\u1eadp v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea5t \u201ct\u1ef1a s\u01a1n \u2013 h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u1ee7y\u201d hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3, <strong data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"277\">Khu Monaco<\/strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ph\u00e2n khu \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n <strong data-start=\"330\" data-end=\"354\">Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong>. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecba th\u1ebf ba m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n c\u00f9ng t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn kho\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea1t bao tr\u1ecdn v\u1ecbnh Nam Ch\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e8o H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng si\u00eau sang, g\u1ee3i nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng xa hoa c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c Monaco b\u00ean b\u1edd \u0110\u1ecba Trung H\u1ea3i.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-48\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khu Monaco \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch v\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 1.000 c\u0103n bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 \u0111\u01a1n l\u1eadp v\u00e0 bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 bi\u1ec3n si\u00eau sang c\u00f3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch r\u1ed9ng, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf tinh x\u1ea3o, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh ri\u00eang t\u01b0 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ph\u00e2n khu c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ebfn du thuy\u1ec1n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, khu clubhouse sang tr\u1ecdng, trung t\u00e2m wellness &amp; spa cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c ti\u1ec7n \u00edch chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o n\u00ean tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ed1ng \u201cresort trong resort\u201d, n\u01a1i c\u01b0 d\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eebng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-49\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u1eeb <strong data-start=\"1090\" data-end=\"1104\">Khu Monaco<\/strong> kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00e2n khu c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n m\u1edf l\u1ed1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ra bi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 b\u1ebfn du thuy\u1ec1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u201ct\u1ecda \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0ng\u201d cho c\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n y\u00eau th\u00edch l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u, \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 ri\u00eang t\u01b0 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn chu\u1ed7i ti\u1ec7n \u00edch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-18 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" alt=\"Ph\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201cthi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng\u201d mi\u1ec1n Trung, v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n c\u1ea3nh quan nguy\u00ean s\u01a1 v\u00e0 b\u1edd bi\u1ec3n xanh ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch.\" title=\"phoi-canh-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-thien-duong-nghi-duong-mien-trung-thiet-ke-hien-dai-canh-quan-nguyen-so-bo-bien-xanh-ngoc.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/phoi-canh-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-thien-duong-nghi-duong-mien-trung-thiet-ke-hien-dai-canh-quan-nguyen-so-bo-bien-xanh-ngoc.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/phoi-canh-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-thien-duong-nghi-duong-mien-trung-thiet-ke-hien-dai-canh-quan-nguyen-so-bo-bien-xanh-ngoc.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5436\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201920%201080%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/phoi-canh-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-thien-duong-nghi-duong-mien-trung-thiet-ke-hien-dai-canh-quan-nguyen-so-bo-bien-xanh-ngoc.jpg-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/phoi-canh-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-thien-duong-nghi-duong-mien-trung-thiet-ke-hien-dai-canh-quan-nguyen-so-bo-bien-xanh-ngoc.jpg-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/phoi-canh-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-thien-duong-nghi-duong-mien-trung-thiet-ke-hien-dai-canh-quan-nguyen-so-bo-bien-xanh-ngoc.jpg-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/phoi-canh-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-thien-duong-nghi-duong-mien-trung-thiet-ke-hien-dai-canh-quan-nguyen-so-bo-bien-xanh-ngoc.jpg-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/phoi-canh-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-thien-duong-nghi-duong-mien-trung-thiet-ke-hien-dai-canh-quan-nguyen-so-bo-bien-xanh-ngoc.jpg-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/phoi-canh-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-thien-duong-nghi-duong-mien-trung-thiet-ke-hien-dai-canh-quan-nguyen-so-bo-bien-xanh-ngoc.jpg.jpg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-50\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ph\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201cthi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng\u201d mi\u1ec1n Trung, v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n c\u1ea3nh quan nguy\u00ean s\u01a1 v\u00e0 b\u1edd bi\u1ec3n xanh ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-51\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>V\u1edbi quy ho\u1ea1ch kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf tinh hoa v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, <strong data-start=\"1451\" data-end=\"1465\">Khu Monaco<\/strong> kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ph\u00e2n khu an c\u01b0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho gi\u1edbi si\u00eau gi\u00e0u, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 <strong data-start=\"1533\" data-end=\"1554\">bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng xa hoa<\/strong> kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay tr\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 n\u01a1i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m, n\u01a1i m\u1ed7i bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec7t t\u00e1c mang gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-13 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background hundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-background-color:#ff5ac0;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"width:104% !important;max-width:104% !important;margin-left: calc(-4% \/ 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% \/ 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-17 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-c