ec1n Vinclub:<\/strong> Gia nh\u1eadp c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u, t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i ti\u1ec7n \u00edch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n.<\/li>\n<li><strong>T\u1ed1i \u01b0u l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn:<\/strong> Chi\u1ebft kh\u1ea5u thanh to\u00e1n s\u1edbm l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 10%, gia t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 sinh l\u1eddi b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i an c\u01b0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n gia t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb theo th\u1eddi gian. \u0110\u1eebng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 sinh l\u1eddi h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn n\u00e0y!<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-55\">    <div class=\"bcp-root\">\n      <form class=\"bcp-overview\">\n        <h3>B\u1ea2NG T\u00cdNH CHI\u1ebeT KH\u1ea4U & THANH TO\u00c1N<\/h3>\n        <div id=\"bcp-overview-grid\" class=\"bcp-grid\">\n          <label data-static=\"1\">T\u00ean kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng:\n            <input name=\"kh_name\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n A\">\n          <\/label>\n          <label data-static=\"1\">Ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch mua:\n            <select id=\"bcp-type\" class=\"bcp-input\"><\/select>\n          <\/label>\n          <div id=\"bcp-overview-dynamic\" class=\"bcp-grid\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/form>\n\n      <div class=\"bcp-tabs\">\n        <button data-tab=\"Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00c1n Kh\u00f4ng Vay\" data-plan=\"I.1 Kh\u00f4ng vay\" class=\"active\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00c1n Kh\u00f4ng Vay<\/button>\n        <button data-tab=\"Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00c1n C\u00f3 Vay\" data-plan=\"I.2 C\u00f3 vay\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00c1n C\u00f3 Vay<\/button>\n        <button data-tab=\"Thanh To\u00e1n S\u1edbm 95%\" data-plan=\"